46
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:54,610
Oh my!

47
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:57,400
That's great.

48
00:06:58,080 --> 00:07:00,280
The shopkeeper has finally found love.

49
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:01,280
Nonsense.

50
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:03,520
The shopkeeper has lived for a thousand years.

51
00:07:03,520 --> 00:07:06,040
And now blooming like an iron tree for this intern.

52
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:06,600
No way.

53
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:07,240
Look.

54
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:24,120
For a thousand years,

55
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:27,200
