124
00:12:20,160 --> 00:12:21,490
I've heard a little bit.

125
00:12:23,680 --> 00:12:26,340
What happened to all of you a thousand years ago?

126
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:28,040
Why did the innkeeper want to kill me?

127
00:12:28,040 --> 00:12:28,960
When I came to the inn,

128
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:31,440
you had already been dealt with by the innkeeper.

129
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:33,000
By that time, the inn was already

130
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,920
under the innkeeper's management.

131
00:12:34,920 --> 00:12:35,600
Haha!

132
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:40,500
As for me...

133
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:42,880
I arrived later than that bootlicker,

134
00:12:42,880 --> 00:12:43,940
so I know even less.

135
00:12:44,880 --> 00:12:47,240
Besides, I've been staying at this Monster Inn

136
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:48,480
just waiting for the innkeeper

137
00:12:48,480 --> 00:12:49,800
to break the curse

138
00:12:49,920 --> 00:12:50,800
and vanish into thin air,

139
00:12:50,800 --> 00:12:51,920
so I can inherit this business.

140
00:12:51,920 --> 00:12:52,250
Oh my,

141
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:53,480
you shouldn't say that!

142
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:54,680
Vanish into thin air?

143
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:57,210
Isn't the innkeeper immortal?

144
00:12:59,160 --> 00:12:59,760
Dongfang,

145
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:01,440
we've only heard rumors.

146
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:03,600
The innkeeper, because of a curse,

147
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:06,760
has been trapped in this Monster Inn for a thousand years.

148
00:13:06,760 --> 00:13:07,680
If by chance,

149
00:13:07,880 --> 00:13:09,280
once the curse is broken,

150
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:10,880
the innkeeper will...

151
00:13:10,880 --> 00:13:11,810
What do you mean?

152
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:13,020
What curse?

153
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:15,480
I really don't know.

154
00:13:15,760 --> 00:13:16,920
I was just making it up.

155
00:13:16,920 --> 00:13:18,680
Please don't slip up and tell the manager.

156
00:13:18,680 --> 00:13:19,160
Right.

157
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:20,920
We just accidentally

158
00:13:20,920 --> 00:13:22,840
overheard the conversation between the medium and the manager.

159
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:24,720
What if this curse isn't real?

160
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,320
What if it's just a legend?

161
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:26,720
Right?

162
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:27,600
Haha.

163
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,330
This is impossible.

164
00:13:31,560 --> 00:13:32,280
Mr. Dongfang.

165
00:13:32,280 --> 00:13:33,080
Mr. Dongfang.

166
00:13:33,400 --> 00:13:34,000
It's over.

167
00:13:34,040 --> 00:13:34,640
It's over.

168
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:36,080
It's all your fault for talking too much.

169
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,360
I didn't do it on purpose.

170
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:39,020
Well, I did it on purpose then.

171
00:13:39,560 --> 00:13:40,800
Oh my!

172
00:13:46,920 --> 00:13:47,480
Ling Po.

173
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:49,850
I have something to ask you.

174
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:52,600
Manager Dongfang.

175
00:13:52,880 --> 00:13:53,800
I didn't expect

176
00:13:54,040 --> 00:13:55,680
we would meet again so soon.

177
00:13:57,560 --> 00:13:59,360
Why was Shangguan Feiye cursed?

178
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:01,280
Why is she burned by karmic fire?

179
00:14:01,280 --> 00:14:01,960
After the curse is lifted,

180
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:04,020
will she really vanish into thin air?

181
00:14:04,840 --> 00:14:06,440
So you've heard everything.

182
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,440
So all of this is true.

183
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:13,280
Not entirely.

184
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:14,880
Ling Po,

185
00:14:15,280 --> 00:14:16,810
please tell me everything.

186
00:14:18,880 --> 00:14:19,920
Shangguan

187
00:14:20,120 --> 00:14:21,560
was indeed cursed.

188
00:14:21,680 --> 00:14:24,480
That's how she became the owner of the Monster Inn.

189
00:14:24,880 --> 00:14:26,480
Ageless and immortal.

190
00:14:27,320 --> 00:14:29,320
But she's trapped in the Monster Inn

191
00:14:29,480 --> 00:14:32,000
because of the mistakes she made in the past.

192
00:14:34,680 --> 00:14:35,880
A thousand years ago,

193
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:37,480
Shangguan Feiye

194
00:14:37,480 --> 00:14:40,080
was the strongest monster hunter in the world.

195
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:43,540
She made it her mission to kill all monsters.

196
00:14:44,160 --> 00:14:45,560
Regardless of whether they were good or evil,

197
00:14:45,560 --> 00:14:46,690
she killed them all.

198
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:50,960
Eventually, because of her excessive killing,

199
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:53,600
the resentment of the monsters she killed backfired on her,

200
00:14:53,600 --> 00:14:54,880
cursing her.

201
00:14:55,880 --> 00:14:58,840
Every so often, she's burned by karmic fire.

202
00:14:59,120 --> 00:15:00,450
The pain is unbearable.

203
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:02,930
At the same time,

204
00:15:03,400 --> 00:15:05,160
the curse also made her someone who could

205
00:15:05,160 --> 00:15:08,220
resolve the obsessions of her guests as the innkeeper.

206
00:15:08,280 --> 00:15:10,210
This is how she atones for her sins.

207
00:15:10,880 --> 00:15:13,320
Being the innkeeper, for her,

208
00:15:13,880 --> 00:15:15,080
is both a curse

209
00:15:15,720 --> 00:15:18,160
and also a form of protection.

210
00:15:19,400 --> 00:15:21,860
So after all these obsessions are resolved,

211
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:24,880
will she really vanish into thin air?
